<item>
            <title>[LU-2329] Test failure on test suite sanity-quota, subtest test_7c</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2329</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;My Patch does not touch sanity-quota at all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Update not seen after 90s: wanted &apos;glb&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;,slv&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;,reint&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&apos; got &apos;glb&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;,slv&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;,reint&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
 sanity-quota test_7c: @@@@@@ FAIL: reintegration failed &lt;br/&gt;
  Trace dump:&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:3865:error_noexit()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:3888:error()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-quota.sh:1060:test_7c()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4143:run_one()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4173:run_one_logged()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:4031:run_test()&lt;br/&gt;
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-quota.sh:1070:main()This issue was created by maloo for wangdi &amp;lt;di.wang@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b59c91b8-2e6a-11e2-a830-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b59c91b8-2e6a-11e2-a830-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_7c failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;reintegration failed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-quota 7c&lt;/p&gt;</description>
